<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I strongly suggest to give full control over the method of validating {{Zend_Form_Element_Multi}} elements!</p>

<p>As for now validators are run on <em>each and every</em> selected value, but there is no way to validate THE WHOLE FIELD, nor give it a GLOBAL SINGLE custom error message.</p>

<p>Current architecture does not allow i.e. to create a {{Zend_Validate_Count}} which would throw error if less (or more) number of fields have been selected. It also is buggy (see ZF-5603 and ZF-5412).</p>

